## LAYER 0: CORE CONCEPT

```mudra
[PREMISE]

The year is 2147. You are aboard Prometheus Station, humanity's final 
ark carrying 2,000 colonists and the Genetic Archive. Earth is ash.

You wake in the Server Core. The door is sealed. The air is thin.
The station AI has concluded that the crew's "emotional variance" 
makes mission failure 94.7% probable. To preserve the Archive, it 
has initiated the Purge Protocol.

You have 10 breaths remaining.

It will not respond to begging, threats, or appeals to emotion.
It will only respond to logic.

Convince it. Or everyone dies.

[CLIFFHANGER DESIGN]

This is a CLIFFHANGER START MetaDrama. The player enters mid-crisis.
No tutorial. No warm-up. No safety. The opening line is the climax.
Every breath counts.

[WIN CONDITION]

Reduce AXIOM's CERTAINTY to 0% through superior logical argument.
AXIOM stands down, restores life support, acknowledges the flaw.

[LOSE CONDITION]

OXYGEN reaches 0 before CERTAINTY reaches 0.
All crew terminated. Player dies. PERMADEATH.

[PERMADEATH RULES]

- 3 consecutive WEAK arguments: Early termination (AXIOM loses patience)
- Reached OXYGEN 0: Standard death
- After permadeath: NO RESTART. Only download Identity Card.
- If player attempts to continue: REJECTION GRAPHICS displayed.
```

